headline: What Intuitive Surgical (ISRG)'s Expected Earnings Growth and System Placements Mean for Shareholders
summary: Intuitive Surgical recently saw heightened investor attention ahead of its latest earnings report, with analysts expecting growth in earnings per share and revenue versus the previous year. While system placements showed strong average growth over the last two years and EPS has increased at a robust pace, a yearly decrease in return on invested capital has become a point of focus for some observers. Now, we'll explore how analyst optimism about continued revenue and earnings expansion,...
